text: Coi Leray Collins (born May 11, 1997) is an American rapper and singer. ==Works== Leray has released two mixtapes: Everythingcoz in 2018 and EC2 (2019). Her debut extended play, Now or Never, was released in 2020. In 2021, the remix of her single, "No More Parties" (featuring Lil Durk), reached the top 40 on the Billboard Hot 100. It was certified platinum by the Recording Industry Association of America (RIAA). In 2022, Leray released her first studio album Trendsetter. The album has her collaborative single with Nicki Minaj, "Blick Blick".
